    "This question made the gypsy shudder.--*Paris*",
    "La Esmeralda smiled, sighed, and remained silent.--*Paris*",
    "Silence ensued.--*Paris*",
    "Gringoire slashed the table with his knife.--*Paris*",
    "The young girl smiled and seemed to be gazing through the wall at something.--*Paris*",
    "All at once she began to sing in a barely articulate voice,----*Paris*",
