    "The unhappy girl fell back on her criminal's seat, speechless, tearless, white as a wax figure.--*Paris*",
    "The president bent down to a man at his feet, who wore a gold cap and a black gown, a chain on his neck and a wand in his hand.--*Paris*",
    "All eyes turned towards a small door, which opened, and, to the great agitation of Gringoire, gave passage to a pretty goat with horns and hoofs of gold.--*Paris*",
