    "In the meantime, although the sun had not yet risen, it was broad daylight; a beautiful rose color enlivened the ancient, decayed chimneys of the Pillar-House.--*Paris*",
    "It was the hour when the earliest windows of the great city open joyously on the roofs.--*Paris*",
    "Some workmen, a few fruit-sellers on their way to the markets on their asses, began to traverse the Gr\u00e8ve; they halted for a moment before this group of soldiers clustered round the Rat-Hole, stared at it with an air of astonishment and passed on.--*Paris*",
    "The recluse had gone and seated herself by her daughter, covering her with her body, in front of her, with staring eyes, listening to the poor child, who did not stir, but who kept murmuring in a low voice, these words only, \"Phoebus!--*Paris*",
    "Phoebus!\"--*Paris*",
    "In proportion as the work of the demolishers seemed to advance, the mother mechanically retreated, and pressed the young girl closer and closer to the wall.--*Paris*",
