    "Then she aroused from the depression into which she had fallen during the last few moments, cried out, and as she spoke, her voice now rent the ear like a saw, then stammered as though all kind of maledictions were pressing to her lips to burst forth at once.--*Paris*",
    "Then, addressing Tristan, foaming at the mouth, with wild eyes, all bristling and on all fours like a female panther,----*Paris*",
