    "She threw herself upon it, she tried to hold it back; she scratched the stone with her nails, but the massive block, set in movement by six men, escaped her and glided gently to the ground along the iron levers.--*Paris*",
    "The mother, perceiving an entrance effected, fell down in front of the opening, barricading the breach with her body, beating the pavement with her head, and shrieking with a voice rendered so hoarse by fatigue that it was hardly audible,----*Paris*",
    "The mother gazed at the soldiers in such formidable fashion that they were more inclined to retreat than to advance.--*Paris*",
