    "The mother offered no resistance, only she dragged herself towards her daughter and threw herself bodily upon her.--*Paris*",
    "The gypsy beheld the soldiers approach.--*Paris*",
    "The horror of death reanimated her,----*Paris*",
    "Rennet Cousin grasped the young girl by the middle of her body, beneath her beautiful shoulders.--*Paris*",
