    "and fainted.--*Paris*",
    "The executioner who was shedding large tears upon her, drop by drop, was about to bear her away in his arms.--*Paris*",
    "He tried to detach the mother, who had, so to speak, knotted her hands around her daughter's waist; but she clung so strongly to her child, that it was impossible to separate them.--*Paris*",
    "Then Rennet Cousin dragged the young girl outside the cell, and the mother after her.--*Paris*",
